comments: Braun (DEN) brings his hands towards Ivey (DET) and marginal contact occurs as Ivey cuts across the perimeter.
Cunningham (DET) brings his forearm towards Braun's (DEN) front and marginal contact occurs as Cunningham releases away from the contact.
Braun (DEN) is drawn into the air towards Cunningham (DET) and marginal contact occurs during the shot attempt.
Porter Jr. (DEN) steps slightly forward towards Thompson (DET) and marginal contact occurs as the defenders switch.
Gordon (DEN) is already in Cunningham's (DET) path when contact occurs and he absorbs the contact to his upper body.

Cunningham (DET) moves into Gordon (DEN) while he is airborne and initiates contact prior to Gordon gaining control of the ball.  While the Nuggets are in the bonus, Gordon would have received two free throws but continuation should not have been granted.
Livers (DET) inbounds the ball within five seconds.
Cunningham (DET) brings his hands towards Caldwell-Pope (DEN) and marginal contact occurs as he releases away to receive the inbounds pass.
Porter Jr. (DEN) cleanly blocks Stewart's (DET) shot near the rim.
Stewart (DET) cleanly blocks Jackson's (DEN) driving shot attempt.
Thompson (DET) does not bring his hand under the ball when he brings his dribble to a pause.
Thompson (DET) receives the ball in the lane and turns to shoot within three seconds.
Gordon (DEN) lowers his arm and makes contact with Thompson's (DET) hand that is not on the ball, and the contact affects his shot near the rim.
Thompson (DET) and Gordon (DEN) briefly engage and disengage as they pursue the rebound.
Stewart (DET) is moving alongside Gordon's (DEN) path and marginal contact occurs as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Braun (DEN) makes clean contact with the ball to momentarily dislodge it from Cunningham (DET) in the backcourt.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) maintains verticality and absorbs the contact from Cunningham (DET) as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Gordon (DEN) cleanly deflects the ball away from Thompson (DET) during the rebound.
Thompson (DET) commits a take foul on Jackson (DEN).
Umude (DET) releases the inbounds pass within five seconds.
Livers (DET) is already in Watson's (DEN) path and marginal contact occurs as the defenders switch during the inbound.
Watson (DEN) cleanly blocks Livers' (DET) jump shot attempt.
